Experience the excitement of Grand Prix glory as your sleek, shiny new racing machine scorches the track with its fire- spitting speed. Four-wheel, independent suspension driving will fool your senses into thinking you're strapped into a real driver's seat. Suped-up 3D graphics a la Dreamcast quality will stroke your eye with incredible detail, including true-to-life twisted-metal damage, spectacular lighting, with all-weather effects. Customize your championship  run with 22 cars to choose from and 15 car settings, and compete against up to 11 opponents in head-to-head mode.